room_title: Escape room "Dark Carnival" by MetaCog Escape Games in Hutchinson
room_description:
Barnaby's Carnival was one of the most successful attractions during the Roaring 20's. With games, music, the Infamous Freakshow, and Gazo the Clown, the carnival was the place to be. Unfortunately, it all came to a close when an accidental fire occurred where there were multiple casualties, including Gazo.
You and your friends have been dared to stay in Barnaby's Carnival for 60 minutes. However, while at the Carnival, you start to hear chuckles in the distance and begin to feel that you're being watched...Can you and your friends escape in 60 minutes before the last laugh is had?
